text: Phryneta aurivillii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hintz in 1913. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo and Cameroon.BioLib.cz - Phryneta aurivillii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1913
